verbose_text: The majority of the BA group showed grade 3 positive VEGF expression in zone 1, 2 and 3 of the hepatocytes in liver biopsy (42.9% for each) (p < 0.05), while the majority of the non BA group showed negative staining of VEGF in zone 1, 2 and 3 of the hepatocytes (68.4%, 68.4%, 71.0% respectively) in liver tissues (p < 0.05) (XREF_TABLE).
